Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.geoweb.web

Interface IGenerator<T>

Type Parameters:
T - - the type of elements created by this generator.
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseStatGenerator, CompositeGenerator, ConstGenerator, IterableGenerator, RandomListGenerator, StatGenerator
public interface IGenerator<T>
This interface represents the abstraction of a queue-factory that generates a (potenentially infinite) number of instances on demand in a specific order. The order of generation may rely on the time - e.g. new entities are generated and cached every 5 seconds. In this case the generator relies on an external caller to periodically notify it of the time - see the
invalid reference 
IGenerator.notifyOfTime
method.
Author:
nikolay.grozev
